data.description: You'll love it the minute you walk in. From the front door this home says Welcome.  Tastefully remodeled recently with updated hickory cabinetry in the kitchen.   Newer flooring adds to the openness of this move in ready home.  Fully fenced for the 4 legged friends and a detached garage is accessed through the alley.  Metal roofing and siding will provide the protection needed from our Northwest  Oklahoma weather. Access to the storm cellar is indoors. Over 1700 square feet this home is priced to move quickly so put this one on your short list.
